# Gitignored files to copy from the source worktree into new worktrees.
# Consumed by `git worktreeinclude apply` (https://github.com/satococoa/git-worktreeinclude).
# Uses gitignore syntax. Only files that are BOTH matched here AND classified
# as ignored by git are copied — tracked files are never touched.
#
# Keep this list minimal: only things a developer/agent literally needs to
# run the app or tests in a fresh worktree. Regeneratable artifacts (e.g.
# `.venv/`, Xcode build output) must NOT be listed; let each worktree build
# its own.

# Backend env — required by pydantic-settings to import `app.config`, which
# every unit test, the server, and the worker depend on.
/sevino-api/.env

# iOS debug xcconfig — required by `xcodebuild` to compile the app in a fresh
# worktree (referenced by Info.plist build settings). Only debug; staging and
# release xcconfigs hold prod credentials and must NOT be copied across.
/sevino-app/Sevino/Config.debug.xcconfig
